                    <h5 class="card-title">Metro Medical Center</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">State-of-the-art medical facility with expert healthcare professionals.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="~/images/hospital3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Hospital 3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Community Health Center</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Dedicated to providing quality healthcare services to the community.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
